room_title: Escape room "Search and Rescue" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: Luke was a great game master. It was the best escape experience I've had at an escape room. Luke really brought the character he played to life, and it helped get me in the right mindset for Search & Rescue.

room_title: Escape room "Search and Rescue" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: These rooms are so much fun! We escaped Search and Rescue today! I can't wait to try the next one.

room_title: Escape room "Search and Rescue" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: Did the Search and Rescue room with four of us all together. It was original and fun, beat it with eight minutes to spare! Can't wait to try some of the more challenging rooms next!
